HOURBOUR QC CRITERIA
Standard 3-pass QC for every Hourbour batch: 
Clarity check — IT image clean and uncluttered? Does it communicate trust? Brand fit check — does it look like a modern fintech product, not a bank or stock photo? No-cliché check — zero coins, piggy banks, cash stacks, or "businessman handshake" imagery? 
